OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with any mist
OL,6,Fand fog quickly lifting. Staying dry
OL,7,Fand fine this afternoon with plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine at first, although cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing a little towards dusk.
OL,10,FFeeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe odd shower possible in
OL,13,Fthe east this evening, otherwise
OL,14,Flargely dry. Low cloud will move into
OL,15,Feastern areas, but clear spells
OL,16,Fcontinuing elsewhere allowing it to
OL,17,Fturn chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
