OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,6,Fwest but cloud in the east will
OL,7,Fcontinue to spread across the region,
OL,8,Fgiving a rather grey afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling cooler than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,12,Fand sunny but breezy for many on
OL,13,FWednesday and Thursday although a risk
OL,14,Fof showers in western Cornwall. Shower
OL,15,Frisk becoming more widespread on
OL,16,FFriday and feeling more humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
